text: i truly enjoy the quality of the material , it holds up excellent in the laundry , and the fact i can order my husband workout gear as well ...{that fits him great by the way} ..is awesome.. easy ordering and fast shipping VIP membership keeps me up to date with the lastest FAB GEAR and workout outfits... i Appreciate You Kate Hudson and and your FABletics family ...Fabletics Keeps me looking and Feeling FABULOUS!!!
